Layer 2 — Transparent Decision Intelligence (ProofSettle)
ProofSettle extends the value of TxLINE by introducing a transparent Decision Intelligence Layer between verified sports intelligence and trustless settlement.
Rather than changing how prediction or settlement works, ProofSettle transforms verified sports intelligence into trusted operational decisions through deterministic business rules, cryptographic validation and transparent decision intelligence.
