Trust Receipt
The story of ProofSettle began with a World Cup fan asking one simple question.
"How do I know this decision genuinely followed the transparent journey you described?"
ProofSettle answers that question through the Trust Receipt.
Every completed settlement generates a Trust Receipt that opens a transparent window into the complete decision journey.
Rather than asking users to simply trust the platform, the Trust Receipt allows anyone to inspect how a specific operational decision was reached—from verified sports intelligence, standardized schemas, smart contract rule evaluation, decision validation, cryptographic verification and final settlement.
Every Trust Receipt includes:
•	Decision ID 
•	Match Information 
•	Rule Evaluation Summary 
•	Verified Sports Intelligence References 
•	Standardized Decision Metadata 
•	Merkle Root 
•	Merkle Proof References 
•	Settlement Transaction 
•	Timestamp 
•	Verification Metadata 
The Trust Receipt enables users to independently understand, verify and validate every decision long after settlement has completed.
